title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Groningen - Eelde Airport and city
description:
In this video we will have a look at both Eelde Airport and the city of Groningen which received an update. Both updates are created by the same developer and add a lot of detail to both the city and the airport. Both the airport and city are stil under development. The city itself contains more then 20 handcrafted objects and the developer already provided some insides that there is more to come.

If you also want to give these addons a try download them via the links below:

Groningen Eelde airport:
https://flightsim.to/file/28878/ehgg-airport-groningen-eelde-the-ntherlands

Groningen city:
https://flightsim.to/file/28873/jhd-groningen-stad

UMCG helipad:
https://flightsim.to/file/28875/ehug-helipad-on-top-of-the-hospital-umcg-in-groningen-the-netherlands

PH-UMC | Dutch Air Ambulance | Mobiel Medisch Team:
https://flightsim.to/file/9832/ph-umc-dutch-air-ambulance-mobiel-medisch-team-8k-h-135
